[DhtmlXQ_comment0]sg 20120507 1980 cnxqtc GM Lv Qin W GM Wang Jialiang D30||ECCO D30 Central Cannon without 3rd Pawn Advancement vs Left Cannon blockade with halfway opposite direction cannons||ECCO:D30 ??????????????||||This game was the one of the few boards that I found which was actually commented by GM Lv Qin himself. His comments are given in quoation marks. ||||"In the 1980 Team championships held in the first half of the year, teams were divided into three groups. In each group, players tried to earn points for their respective teams and only the top  four players of each group were able to advance into the 'A' group. ||After 11 rounds of fierce competition, I emerged as second place in my group and was able to take part in the next round.||Players in next round included Xiangi greats like Hu Ronghua, Yang Guanlin (Lv's mentor), Liu Dahua, Li Laiqun, Wang Jialiang, Xu Tianli, Chen Xiaokun, Zang Ruyi, Yan Mujiang, Hu Yuanmao and Li Richun. I was the youngest amongst all the players, and maybe because I had nothing to lose, I played without fear and for the first time in my life, I was able to defeat the likes of Hu Ronghua and Wang Jialiang.||This game was an epic battle which I played against GM Wang Jialiang."[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
